Still genes my count for what 20-30% of it. What is 50% or more is condidance. And these girls know they have it. Hell, the world it telling them they have it (yes i know there are insecurities and they compare themselves to other models  yet they know they are part of a select few&#8211;talking on a globally ).<br />
Heels give u long legs but these girls look just as good barefooted.<br />
One of the my most powerful style memories is seeing this french (yes, i know , the french) lady in bucharest in the summer; She had on a light white shirt, light linen cargo pants and flat sandals. This was surely more than 5 years ago and I can still see it perfectly. Though I still haven&#8217;t found such a perfect fitting pair of summer pants (might have something to do with the thighs i&#8217;m trying to fit the pants on) she din&#8217;t have on something that jaw dropping, it was the way she wore it and they way she conducted herself.</p>
